your energy and confidence with V-Boost. If you're feeling tired, weighed down by your belly, or no longer confident in your body, V-Boost was made for you.</p>\n      <p>Thanks to its <strong>Ionic Ice technology</strong>, it not only shapes your body but also boosts circulation, activates your muscles and recharges your energy — so you feel more alive, focused and ready to take on the day.</p>\n      <ul>\n        <li><div><strong>Boosts daily energy</strong> — Ionic Ice tech stimulates circulation and keeps you more awake and energized throughout the day.</div></li>\n        <li><div><strong>Strengthens muscles</strong> — Shapes pectoral &amp; abdominal muscles, making you look more toned.</div></li>\n        <li><div><strong>Reduces gynecomastia</strong> — Tightens the chest and enhances your masculine shape.</div></li>\n        <li><div><strong>Improves posture</strong> — Aligns your back and shoulders, relieving pressure and discomfort.</div></li>\n        <li><div><strong>Comfortable &amp; breathable</strong> — Premium nylon-spandex blend fits like a second skin all day long.</div></li>\n      </ul>\n      <div class=\"quote-box\">\n        <p>\"I dropped 30 lbs in 2 months with V-Boost. It's super comfortable and really boosted my confidence.\"</p>\n        <div class=\"quote-author\">\n          <img class=\"avatar\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0873/2380/3993/files/portrait-homme-affaires-souriant_23-2148746289_2.jpg?v=1724655911\" alt=\"Elie Chamoun\" />\n          <div class=\"author-info\">\n            <strong>Elie Chamoun</strong>\n            <span>Verified buyer</span>\n            <div class=\"stars\">★ ★ ★ ★ ★</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<!-- ── HOW IT WORKS ── -->\n<section class=\"how-section\">\n  <p class=\"section-title\">How V-Boost Works</p>\n  <p class=\"section-subtitle\">Three layers of science-backed technology working together inside every vest.</p>\n  <div class