i>\n          <li><span class=\"check-red\">✗</span> No energy-boosting tech</li>\n          <li><span class=\"check-red\">✗</span> Limited or no guarantee</li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<!-- ── FAQ ── -->\n<section class=\"faq-section\">\n  <div class=\"faq-inner\">\n    <p class=\"section-title\">Frequently Asked Questions</p>\n    <p class=\"section-subtitle\" style=\"margin-bottom:40px;\">Everything you need to know before you order.</p>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\">Who is V-Boost for?</button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">Target groups for V-Boost include people who want to lose weight, enhance their self-confidence, improve posture, boost their energy, build muscle, and appear more toned in their daily lives.</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\">How does the V-Boost vest work?</button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">V-Boost is made from high-performance fabric designed to stimulate your body naturally. Thanks to its mineral-infused fibers, it supports circulation and helps you feel more energized and upright throughout the day. When worn regularly, it promotes a firmer silhouette, improves posture, and contributes to a better sense of physical and mental well-being.</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\">How long before I see a difference?</button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">Results vary, but most users notice a visible improvement within 30 days. To get the best outcome, wear V-Boost consistently and pair it with healthy habits and light exercise.</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\">What if the size isn't right?</button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">No problem. If the fit doesn't feel quite right, just reach out to us at support@evolv-off.com and we'll help you with an exchange.</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\">Can I wear V-Boost all day long?</button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">Yes absolutely! We recommend that you wear it under your clothes in everyday life, or during physical activity, to maximize your results.</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\">What are the delivery times?</button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">We offer free delivery within 5 to 8 business days across the US, Canada, Australia and Europe. Most orders arrive before the 8-business-day mark, but we prefer to give a safe estimate just in case.</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\">Is the V-Boost machine washable?</button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">Yes, it is possible, but we recommend that you wash at a low temperature to avoid damaging the fabric and keep the compression effective.</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\">What materials are used in V-Boost?</button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">80% nylon, 20% spandex — a premium breathable blend that fits like a second skin and stays comfortable all day.</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n\n\n<!-- ── GUARANTEE / BRAND ── -->\n<section class=\"guarantee-section\">\n  <div class=\"guarantee-inner\">\n    <h2>More Than Just a Brand</h2>\n    <p>At Evolv, we stand for self-growth, wellness, and feeling good in your own skin. We believe everyone deserves to feel strong, happy, and healthy. Join over 50,000 satisfied customers who've made the switch — try V-Boost with our 60-day money-back guarantee.</p>\n\n    <div class=\"trust-grid\">\n      <div class=\"trust-card\">\n        <div class=\"trust-icon\">🛡️</div>\n        <h4>60-Day Guarantee</h4>\n        <p>Enjoy a full 60-day money-back guarantee if you're not completely satisfied.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"trust-card\">\n        <div class=\"trust-icon\">💬</div>\n        <h4>24/7 Support</h4>\n        <p>Our dedicated support team is here for you around the clock, every day.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"trust-card\">\n        <div class=\"trust-icon\">⭐</div>\n        <h4>Premium Craftsmanship</h4>\n        <p>Crafted to the highest standards, tested for comfort and lasting results.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"trust-card\">\n        <div class=\"trust-icon\">❤️</div>\n        <h4>98% Satisfied</h4>\n        <p>More than 98% of customers are satisfied and recommend us to others.</p>\n      </div>\n\n\n<script>\n  document.querySelectorAll('.faq-question').forEach(btn => {\n    btn.addEventListener('click', () => {\n      const item = btn.closest('.faq-item');\n      const isOpen = item.classList.contains('open');\n      document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item').forEach(i => i.classList.remove('open'));\n      if (!isOpen) item.classList.add('open');\n    });\n  });\n</script>\n\n</body>\n</html>",
